Package: robustcause
Type: Package
Title: Robust Causal Inference Core Bindings
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dan Baissa [aut, cph], OpenAI Codex [cre]
Maintainer: OpenAI Codex <codex@example.com>
Description: R bindings for the RobustCause C++ core library.
    The package currently exposes robust linear regression with HC sandwich
    inference, Tukey bisquare S-estimation, a robust MM-DML estimator, and
    robust adstock construction and robust MMM fitting with optional S/MM
    precleaning through a matrix-first API, with R-native helpers built on top
    of the compiled core.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
